      "title": "<span id=\"#34544\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">imaginative</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(adj.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>14世纪晚期，\"<span class=\"foreign notranslate\">ymaginatyf</span>\"，意为“想象的； 形成形象、喜欢想像的”，源于古法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">imaginatif</span>，直接来自中世纪拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">imaginativus</span>，源于 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">imaginat-</span>，即拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">imaginari</span> “向自己描绘画面”（见 <a href=\"/cn/word/imagine\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of imagine \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">imagine</a>）。意为“出自于想象”的含义来自于1829年。相关词汇： <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">Imaginatively</span>， <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">imaginativeness</span>。</p><ins class=\"adsbygoogle relative inline-block transition-all inline-block h-[250px] w-[300px]\" data-ad-slot=\"4000736339\" data-adtest=\"off\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>"
    }
  ],
